  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: Discussion On Making All Things Equal
---
The Way has never known boundaries; speech has no constancy. But
because of [the recognition of a] "this," there came to be boundaries.
Let me tell you what the boundaries are.
